title: iPhone 6s 6s Plus Sales Were 10 to 15% Weaker than iPhone 6's in Japan
text: As reported by Digitimes, Apple's new iPhone 6s and 6s Plus sales numbers were 10-15% lower than the figures for the previous iPhone 6 model during the first weekend after the official release in stores.
